snippet: In the largest attack, two suicide bombers targeted an Iraqi military base north of Baghdad late Thursday, killing 22 soldiers and wounding at least 45 others, officials said.
abstract: Three separate bombing attacks kill at least 30 people in Iraq.
lead_paragraph: In the largest attack, two suicide bombers targeted an Iraqi military base north of Baghdad late Thursday, killing 22 soldiers and wounding at least 45 others, officials said.

headline.main: Iraq: Blasts Kill at Least 30 People
